name: Rogue Drone Infestation Data
description:
This database contains a large quantity of data generated by a CONCORD Rogue Analysis Beacon (CRAB), and describes the detected extent and activities of rogue drone infestations proximate to the CRAB's operating location. 

The data also includes valuable insights into rogue drone technology and behavior gleaned from rogue units attracted to the CRAB's powerful active scan signal.
